OOC:( Where the heck did the Lobstruck come from?)

::DarkMouse::

she hears a noise come from behind her, but in the air.  She turns 
and sees a flying bug coming after her. She transformed into bot 
mode.  She stumbled, but remained standing.  She drew her gun and 
fired on the flying bug.  She turned and ran.
